{{!
    @template local_dimensions/central/structure_related_chips

    The referenced-competency chips for the Structure-tab detail pane. Rendered client-side
    by local_dimensions/central/structure from the local_dimensions_list_related_competencies
    response and injected into the detail-related-list region. Each chip opens the referenced
    competency in a modal (data-action open-related carries the competency id).

    Context variables required:
    * items (array) {id, name} · the related competencies

    Example context (json):
    {
        "items": [
            {"id": 7, "name": "Communication"},
            {"id": 9, "name": "Teamwork"}
        ]
    }
}}
{{#items}}
<button type="button" class="local-dimensions-central-structure-related-chip"
        data-action="open-related" data-id="{{id}}"
        title="{{#str}}central_related_view, local_dimensions{{/str}}">
    <span class="local-dimensions-central-structure-related-chip-name">{{name}}</span>
    <i class="fa fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</button>
{{/items}}
